Radio Skranglebass was the idea that the fall of 2005. 6. January 2006, had his first radio broadcast. Then it was sent directly from the radio release party held at Club PI, Oslo. This is a radio that we want to offer the listener the best of electronic music and mixes from djs and artists. Our focus is to represent the music that is found in club culture in Norway, and promote new and exciting music you do not hear on typical Norwegian radio stations. Based on that more and more people have an affair with electronic music, we have an audience of 15-45 years for both sexes. Radio Skranglebass consists of 100% volunteers and receive no form of government support or money from the fund.
